  49+ 2000
  50+ 2000                              // emulate something like:  ld hl,rp
  51+ 2000              ldhlrp          macro
  52+ 2000 ~                            ld      hl,(RP_Pointer)
  53+ 2000                              endm
  54+ 2000
  55+ 2000                              // emulate something like:  ld rp,hl
  56+ 2000              ldrphl          macro
